WEBVTT

00:01.468 --> 00:03.870
So I sign this and the bribery
allegations are gone?

00:03.904 --> 00:05.537
And no one ever knows
a thing.

00:05.572 --> 00:08.241
You never let me tell you
what the money was for.

00:08.275 --> 00:10.442
You didn't listen to me
when I told you I don't care.

00:10.477 --> 00:12.278
Well, do you care
that after Mike grilled me,

00:12.312 --> 00:15.047
I was so impressed with him that
I wonder why I'd forgotten him?

00:15.082 --> 00:19.685
But I couldn't find any record
of him ever being in my class.

00:19.719 --> 00:21.787
Just like they're not gonna
find any record of you

00:21.821 --> 00:23.655
accepting a bribe
from a student.

00:23.690 --> 00:26.425
Jessica, your secret
is safe with me.

00:27.560 --> 00:29.495
I told him you found out

00:29.529 --> 00:32.264
that I covered up
Daniel Hardman's embezzlement.

00:32.298 --> 00:34.500
And now you want me to protect
another one of your secrets.

00:34.534 --> 00:36.735
It's the same secret, Louis,

00:36.770 --> 00:38.704
and you have just as much
invested in it as I do.

00:38.738 --> 00:40.939
You want me to kiss the ring,
Louis, after what you did?

00:40.973 --> 00:42.340
You're damn right I do,

00:42.375 --> 00:44.276
because I don't care
how it got up there.

00:44.310 --> 00:48.780
My name is on that wall
whether you like it or not.

